{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "Analogous to Eq.",
    "(3), we summed the squared amplitudes corresponding to frequencies inside a bin of amplitude Δω.",
    "Since each signal had a different P T, to compare between subjects and/ or regions, we divided the result by the total power P T and multiplied by 100 to make it a percentage.",
    "Arbitrarily, we chose the parameter Δω for each subject so that each bin included 10% of the total power.",
    "The qualitative results did not depend on the exact choice of the bin width."
  ],
